{"tid":2087964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美推金融法案 涉四大內銀8.5萬億元","createTime":"2020-07-01T02:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:54:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb38c0476ca61ff4b77b55875b196ec922b2a18","tid":2087964,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200701/6LONZ3NRU4LBHOGXCOY322DIMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2F6LONZ3NRU4LBHOGXCOY322DIMY%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=7407f297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2F6LONZ3NRU4LBHOGXCOY322DIMY%2F&h=ac079e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200701/6LONZ3NRU4LBHOGXCOY322DIMY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美推金融法案 涉四大內銀8.5萬億元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OaByIWTTTIWgysknLpk1QkFHPDQ=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VDMV365A6EWSFD3EWJWPG3CATQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOaByIWTTTIWgysknLpk1QkFHPDQ%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVDMV365A6EWSFD3EWJWPG3CATQ.jpg&h=b4acb8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國銀行或受美國金融制裁法案牽連。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共就港版國安法立法，美國打出制裁牌，彭博分析指出，由於美國參、眾兩院正推進一項涉及金融制裁的法案，估計中國四大國有銀行面臨巨額資金風險，涉及1.1萬億美元（約8.53萬億港元），兼可能遭到罰款。<br />\n<br />\n上周四，美國參議院一致通過《香港問責法案》，這條法案原稱《香港自治法案》，以授權美國政府部門通過金融等制裁<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n括禁止向美國金融機構借貸和銀行交易等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析師憂波及全球銀行<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：人治立法 充斥「例外」程序<br />\n<br />\n彭博行<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n令有關銀行也遭到制裁。<br />\n<br />\n參考工行、建行、中行和農行截至去年底的年報，共持有折合約1.1萬億美元的美元負債，當中47%屬於存款，其餘是銀行間同業借款及向全球投資者發行的證券，當制裁成真，這四間國有銀行會陷於巨額的資金風險。<br />\n<br />\n《香港問責法案》距離落實<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n份客戶可能就是被制裁的中國官員及其親友。<br />\n<br />\n美國對其他國家官員進行金融制裁並不鮮見，參考2014年吞併克里米亞的<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n術公司逾30天的債券，禁止投資俄羅斯儲蓄銀行等六間銀行逾30天的債券，及禁止向多間俄資公司出口石油開採相關的商品和服務等。"},{"pid":"3ae4099c9a46c4ffd74dbb5ce9827c022ef6bf65","tid":2087964,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾人打到咁 中共把劍係咪唔見左"},{"pid":"6ebf68a11484b3834afb087bac56fb0e0df4f6fe","tid":2087964,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2mrfadc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2mrfadc.jpg&h=4707d54f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e54ecf49b3e28e0865f42eafe20b24c68d6e8a16","tid":2087964,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"亮劍呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630ee2e25ec708d0aff14e867e593ea6d5154e9b","tid":2087964,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"Visa / master / AE 可能都用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac5b79d0d814e60e5402b6a72b4bb4852e5e729","tid":2087964,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"幾時出招唔承認支那持有嘅所有美債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f126a945c45d2e303e6233df716b6d56cb1dd1af","tid":2087964,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb38c0476ca61ff4b77b55875b196ec922b2a18","tid":2087964,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200701/6LONZ3NRU4LBHOGXCOY322DIMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2F6LONZ3NRU4LBHOGXCOY322DIMY%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&